{"navVariant":"base","head":{"title":"Finance | Moonstone Advocates","description":"Getting the right finance in place can make or break a property deal. That’s where we come in. We help lenders and borrowers across Yorkshire and the UK move quickly and confidently through all kinds of property finance transactions. Whether you’re funding a development, buying a portfolio, or securing a bridging loan, we’ll get to grips with the detail and keep things moving. We’ll work closely with our Banking, Planning and Construction teams to spot potential issues early and tailor everything to your goals.","ogTitle":"Finance | Moonstone Advocates","ogDescription":"Getting the right finance in place can make or break a property deal. That’s where we come in. We help lenders and borrowers across Yorkshire and the UK move quickly and confidently through all kinds of property finance transactions. Whether you’re funding a development, buying a portfolio, or securing a bridging loan, we’ll get to grips with the detail and keep things moving. We’ll work closely with our Banking, Planning and Construction teams to spot potential issues early and tailor everything to your goals.","ogType":"website","twitterCard":"summary_large_image","canonical":"finance.html","jsonLd":["{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\": \"WebPage\",\n  \"name\": \"Finance\",\n  \"description\": \"Getting the right finance in place can make or break a property deal. That’s where we come in. We help lenders and borrowers across Yorkshire and the UK move quickly and confidently through all kinds of property finance transactions. Whether you’re funding a development, buying a portfolio, or securing a bridging loan, we’ll get to grips with the detail and keep things moving. We’ll work closely with our Banking, Planning and Construction teams to spot potential issues early and tailor everything to your goals.\n\",\n  \"url\": \"/for-businesses/business-real-estate/finance\",\n  \"inLanguage\": \"en\",\n  \"dateModified\": \"2026-06-03T09:53:41.064Z\",\n  \"datePublished\": \"2026-06-03T09:54:18.750Z\",\n  \"about\": {\n    \"@type\": \"Service\",\n    \"name\": \"Finance\",\n    \"description\": \"Getting the right finance in place can make or break a property deal. That’s where we come in. We help lenders and borrowers across Yorkshire and the UK move quickly and confidently through all kinds of property finance transactions. Whether you’re funding a development, buying a portfolio, or securing a bridging loan, we’ll get to grips with the detail and keep things moving. We’ll work closely with our Banking, Planning and Construction teams to spot potential issues early and tailor everything to your goals.\n\",\n    \"provider\": {\n      \"@type\": \"LegalService\",\n      \"name\": \"Moonstone Advocates\"\n    },\n    \"serviceType\": \"Real Estate\",\n    \"areaServed\": {\n      \"@type\": \"Country\",\n      \"name\": \"Uganda\"\n    }\n  },\n  \"mainEntity\": {\n    \"@type\": \"FAQPage\",\n    \"mainEntity\": [\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"Can you act for both the lender and the borrower?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"Yes, with informed consent we can act for both parties, provided there’s no conflict and all regulations are followed.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"What types of property do advise on?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"We advise on residential, commercial, mixed-use, and bespoke assets, including specialist sectors such as healthcare and energy.\"\n        }\n      },\n      {\n        \"@type\": \"Question\",\n        \"name\": \"How quickly can bridging finance transactions be completed?\",\n        \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n          \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n          \"text\": \"We understand the urgency of bridging finance and work proactively to meet tight deadlines, often completing within days.\"\n        }\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}"]},"blocks":[{"tag":"main","attrs":{"className":"main-wrapper"},"html":"<header data-wf--02-standard-header--variant=\"dark\" data-wf-component-id=\"949280b8-8e72-c6a2-5bfc-7cfb2eeda9b8\" data-wf-variant-state=\"8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\" class=\"section_header w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div class=\"padding-global is-page-top\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"simple_header_grid\"><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf8719e-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-left\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><h1 class=\"heading-style-h1\">Finance</h1></div><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Getting the right finance in place can make or break a property deal. That’s where we come in. We help lenders and borrowers across Yorkshire and the UK move quickly and confidently through all kinds of property finance transactions. Whether you’re funding a development, buying a portfolio, or securing a bridging loan, we’ll get to grips with the detail and keep things moving. We’ll work closely with our Banking, Planning and Construction teams to spot potential issues early and tailor everything to your goals.\n</p><div class=\"margin-top margin-medium\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a arrow-rotate=\"trigger\" data-btn-hover=\"\" data-theme=\"primary\" href=\"/contact\" class=\"btn is-icon w-inline-block\"><div class=\"btn__bg\"></div><div class=\"btn__circle-wrap\"><div class=\"btn__circle\"><div class=\"before__100\"></div></div></div><div class=\"btn__text\"><p class=\"btn-text-p\">Speak to an expert</p></div><div btn-arrow=\"right\" class=\"arrow is-button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-xsmall w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div></a></div></div></div><div id=\"w-node-_8b2fa05c-57cd-b490-ced6-6fac2cf871aa-2eeda9b8\" class=\"simple_header_grid-right\"><div class=\"simple-header_image-wrapper\"><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"simple_header-component\"><div class=\"padding-section-xsmall\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div data-wf--breadcrumb-original--variant=\"base\" class=\"breadcrumb_component\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">Home</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><a href=\"/for-businesses\" class=\"breadcrumb_link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_page\">For businesses</div></a><div class=\"breadcrumb_icon w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M5 13h11.17l-4.88 4.88c-.39.39-.39 1.03 0 1.42s1.02.39 1.41 0l6.59-6.59a.996.996 0 0 0 0-1.41l-6.58-6.6a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41 1.41L16.17 11H5c-.55 0-1 .45-1 1s.45 1 1 1\"></path></svg></div></div><div class=\"breadcrumb_div\"><div class=\"breadcrumb_current-page\">Finance</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_shape-wrapper w-variant-8c1228b1-e5f0-eb03-34af-789b7e070b17\"><div lottie=\"target-load\" class=\"header_shape is-standard\" data-w-id=\"5d828c84-1f1c-1e38-bfb3-80ffb8d04940\" data-animation-type=\"lottie\" data-src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/69db9824cf9ff19dd03c1c29_08fdbca2c62ae345f765f433c8401fe4_Blacks_V_Blue.json\" data-loop=\"0\" data-direction=\"1\" data-autoplay=\"1\" data-is-ix2-target=\"0\" data-renderer=\"svg\" data-default-duration=\"0\" data-duration=\"0\" data-loading=\"lazy\"></div></div><div class=\"simple-header_background-image-wrapper\"><div class=\"image-overlay-layer\"></div><img loading=\"eager\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/68b448d4e0ae8eda7aa37155_placeholder-image.svg\" alt=\"Grey image placeholder with image icon centralised\" class=\"simple-header_background-image\"></div></header><section class=\"section_benefit-grid_layout\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid benefit-grid_list\"><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Standard commercial lending</h4><p>We’ll guide you through a wide range of commercial finance transactions including investment purchases, owner-occupier finance, and portfolio deals, making sure everything supports your commercial goals while maintaining legal and regulatory compliance.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Bridging loans</h4><p>We move fast on bridging finance transactions, understanding the time critical nature. You’ll get clear advice and proactive support to meet tight deadlines.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Development finance</h4><p>From initial funding to final sign-off, we’ll support your project every step of the way. We work hand in hand with our Planning and Construction teams to keep everything on track.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Financing of bespoke property assets</h4><p>From care homes to sports venues, we help clients finance complex or unusual property assets with solutions tailored to each deal. Our tailored solutions are designed to meet the specific needs of each transaction.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Private Lending</h4><p>We advise on private loan arrangements, including syndicated loans. We provide clear documentation and safeguard the interests of all parties involved.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><h4>Dual representation</h4><p>With the right permissions, we can act for both borrower and lender. It speeds things up while keeping everything transparent and compliant. We ensure both parties receive clear, practical guidance and documentation tailored to the complexity and scale of each transaction.</p><p>‍</p></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div><div class=\"benefit-grid_item w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty w-richtext\"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section_accordion\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"faq6_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_content\"><div class=\"faq6_content-left\"><h2>Questions we’re often asked</h2><div class=\"margin-top margin-small\"><div class=\"button-group\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"button is-secondary w-button\">Speak to an expert</a></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_list\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid faq6_list-grid\"><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f7d\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Can you act for both the lender and the borrower?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Yes, with informed consent we can act for both parties, provided there’s no conflict and all regulations are followed.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f88\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>What types of property do advise on?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>We advise on residential, commercial, mixed-use, and bespoke assets, including specialist sectors such as healthcare and energy.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f93\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>How quickly can bridging finance transactions be completed?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>We understand the urgency of bridging finance and work proactively to meet tight deadlines, often completing within days.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7f9e\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>Do you assist with development finance?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>Yes. We provide full legal support throughout development finance transactions, from initial funding to final drawdown, working closely with our Planning and Construction teams.</p></div></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_accordion\"><div data-w-id=\"2d4f5f46-8657-6adf-b3b2-ede2787f7fa9\" class=\"faq6_question\"><div>What is required for a private loan arrangement?</div><div class=\"faq6_icon-wrapper\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 32 32\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M25.3333 15.667V16.3336C25.3333 16.7018 25.0349 17.0003 24.6667 17.0003H17V24.667C17 25.0351 16.7015 25.3336 16.3333 25.3336H15.6667C15.2985 25.3336 15 25.0351 15 24.667V17.0003H7.3333C6.96511 17.0003 6.66663 16.7018 6.66663 16.3336V15.667C6.66663 15.2988 6.96511 15.0003 7.3333 15.0003H15V7.33365C15 6.96546 15.2985 6.66699 15.6667 6.66699H16.3333C16.7015 6.66699 17 6.96546 17 7.33365V15.0003H24.6667C25.0349 15.0003 25.3333 15.2988 25.3333 15.667Z\" fill=\"currentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div></div><div class=\"faq6_answer\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><p>We ensure all documentation is in place, including loan agreements, security documents, and compliance checks tailored to the transaction.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Andrew Pedley was the driving force at Moonstone LLP. He really made us feel like we were the only case on his desk. No job was too small, and no question was too little to ask. He made me feel like my thoughts and views were valid and also explained situations where I wasn&#x27;t understanding the full picture.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I would just like to say a huge thanks to Conor Tobin and Moonstone. You have really turned this around, and we are very grateful. Looking forward to working with you in the future.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was impressed by the team at Moonstone Advocates. Every member of staff I dealt with was pleasant and professional, demonstrating a clear commitment to helping me rather than just driving up costs.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My first time using Moonstone, I&#x27;ve used a few solicitors over time, working with team at Moonstone has been effortless and efficient, I would be happy to recommend and use again.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">It’s clear that client care and hospitality are taken seriously here. I would highly recommend Moonstone to anyone looking for a professional, welcoming and experienced legal firm.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Very impressed with their experience from start to finish. The legal team were exceptionally friendly, welcoming, and professional throughout. The security staff were particularly polite and approachable, making visitors feel comfortable as soon as they arrived. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Moonstone Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Andrew Pedley was the driving force at Moonstone LLP. He really made us feel like we were the only case on his desk. No job was too small, and no question was too little to ask. He made me feel like my thoughts and views were valid and also explained situations where I wasn&#x27;t understanding the full picture.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">My Direct Dealing has been with Marcus Kaye from Moonstone solicitors, and I can&#x27;t express how thorough and on hand he has been. Marcus has always been my point of contact and has left no stone unturned during my time with Moonstone. Moonstone are renowned for being on many of the bank&#x27;s panels as go to solicitors I trust them completely.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone Advocates are a modern and dynamic practice with the depth of experience and knowledge that gives me the confidence to work with them on any transaction. They have multiple teams with expert knowledge in their respective fields that can be called upon when needed. Everyone there is a genuinely nice person to deal with.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">All the individuals we have dealt with have been professional and conscientious and have met any deadline we have given them.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Real Estate Client</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_team\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"slider-main_component\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-4-card-slider\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_instance\"><h2 data-scroll-speed=\"0.025\" data-scroll=\"\" class=\"heading-style-h2\">Experts in every area</h2><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-4-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div hover-zoom=\"trigger\" class=\"team-member_item\"><a href=\"/our-people/edward-labeja\" class=\"team-member_item w-inline-block\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"team-member_image-wrapper\"><img hover-zoom=\"target\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"/assets/team/placeholder.svg\" class=\"image is-team\"></div></div><div class=\"team-member_text-wrapper\"><div fs-list-field=\"full-name\" class=\"text-size-large text-weight-semibold\">Edward Labeja</div><div class=\"hidden-text\"><div fs-list-field=\"first-name\">Edward</div><div fs-list-field=\"last-name\" class=\"text-size-large text-weight-semibold\">Labeja</div></div><div class=\"article-meta\"><div fs-list-field=\"job-title\" class=\"secondary_tag\">Partner</div></div></div></a></div></div><div fs-sli